description: In this Photo Retouching Tutorial, I will walk you step by step, through the process that I use to make beautiful photographic art! Woo your clients and friends with the beautiful pictures that you can create and maybe even make money doing what you love! I'm a professional photographer with many years of experience in graphic art as well. By combining my skill set with some great software I've been able to achieve fantastic results. I teach creativity and photography workshops to other professional photographers and artists around the country. This is your chance to enjoy learning my most effective methods on How to Retouch Photos at your own pace, and in your own home!
title: The Wonderful World of Digital Art and Photography
